Two rival bidder for Connaught Biosciences come extend deir offer to acquire Toronto based vaccine on Friday.

Institut Merieux S.A. wey carry 942 million dollars (US$801.2 million) or C$37 connaught talk sey e go extend e bid based on expiry on Thursday to Nov. 6.

C$30-a-share wey Ciba-Geigl, one pharmaceutical company wey dey for Basel, Switzerland, and Cal-Associated Chiron Corp. Dem do this one from Nov. 16

E don dey since Friday evening.

Merieux don yarn before sey e go ensure sey e bid, e go open for final decision by Canadian regulator on top wheder e go gree di takeover.

Merieux Vaccine and bioresearch firm wey dey Lyon for France, dey control 50 percent of the state owned Rhone Poulenc S.A.

