Meerieux spokesman yarn last week sey de dey "highly confident" di offer go get approval once e submit details of en proposed investment give Federal Govnor.

Both offer na condition of regulatory approval, and enough na to give di bidders di best wey Connaught get.

Institut Merieux wey don hold di 125% stake for Connaught don yarn sey for di close business Thursday, 5,745,188 share of Connaught and C$44.3 million face di debentures, convertible convertible to 1,826,596 wey get value.

Near di close of business Thursday, na im Ciba-Geigy and Chiron come yarn sey na 11,580 main share dem don dey get since dem start to share di money.

Last report, Connaught get 21.8 million share.

Separation aside, Ontario Supreme Court yarn sey e go postpone indefinitely on top di lawsuit wey dey ground by University of Toronto against Connaught in connection with Merieux bid.

For one statement wey lawyer for University and Connaught, di parties gree sey dem go reach one C415 million research agreement, sey e dey unnecessary make judgement on top di matter of di case at dis time.

Law wey dey for di two side no dey quick get comment.

Di university don seek one injunction wey go block Connaught board from recommendation, or support one offer for di company by Merieux.

